en_481374_0	11 Division HQ under command to the Security Force HQ - Central organized a lecture on 'mental balance & improvement' on Wednesday (6) at the 11 Division headquarters in Pallekele, Kandy.
en_481374_1	The lecture was conducted by Lieutenant Colonel Samantha of Sri Lanka Army's Directorate of Psychological Operations.
en_481374_2	The main intention of the lecture was to improve the positive thinking among them for life progress and own improvements.
en_481374_3	20 officers and 250 other ranks attended the awareness programme.
